  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to collect and manifest earth release chakra until it laces the striking portion of your weapon. The earth release chakra  begins to magnify the weight and striking power of your attacks allowing you tear through anything in your path is little difficulty.<br /></p><p>Make a single ranged taijutsu attack against one creature you can see within range, this jutsu cannot score a critical hit. On a hit, you deal your weapons damage + 1d12 earth damage and the target is pushed back 5 feet.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank  increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the  damage by 1d12. </p>",
